    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, powered by the high-revving S54 inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and structural subframe reinforcement to mitigate common chassis fatigue. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping profile with updated bushings for sharpened turn-in response. Mechanically robust and thermally efficient, this example represents a balanced platform for the discerning enthusiast.",
